{"ItemName":"Bioinformatics Algorithms (Part 1) ","Major":"Computer Science: Theory Biology & Life Sciences ","LinkUrl":"https://www.coursera.org/course/bioinformatics","Content":"<p><span class="GingerNoCheckStart"></span>The sequencing of the&nbsp;human genome a decade ago&nbsp;fueled a computational revolution
    in biology, which&nbsp;has arguably been an impetus for more new&nbsp;algorithms
