    help us explore algorithms applied to&nbsp;a wide range of biological topics,
    from finding regulatory motifs&nbsp;to reconstructing the tree of life.&nbsp; Throughout
    the process, we will apply&nbsp;<i>real</i> bioinformatics algorithms to&nbsp;<i>real</i> genetic
    data.</p>
